## Related Wait Types

| Wait Type | Relationship |
|---|---|
| `PAGEIOLATCH_SH` | Reading data pages from disk — usually appears alongside IO_COMPLETION |
| `PAGEIOLATCH_EX` | Writing data pages to disk |
| `ASYNC_IO_COMPLETION` | Similar to IO_COMPLETION but for background tasks |
| `WRITELOG` | Transaction log write waits — check if log disk is also slow |
| `BACKUPIO` | Backup I/O competing with data I/O |

